	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64158393"><p>These aren't really batteries, they're electronuclear cells. We make batteries by putting together multiple electrochemical cells, and you could do the same thing here. The real problem is that they're not very energy dense.</p><p>You could improve that pretty easily. The problem then is that is the higher you make the energy density the more dangerous they get.</p></div>
	</div>

